Statement: expression';' {...}
  | declaration

######IF/ELSE Example

```  
// Else example
val x = 1;
if (x) {
  x = 5;
}
else {
  x = 10;
}
```

######Build the tree for this code:

```
Block
  '='
    'x'
    random
      lit(2)
  'If' // need unique label #, 
    var(x)
    BLOCK
      '='
        'x'
        lit(5) // archive, decrement scope
    Block (Else) // block b/c we have open curly brace, add 1 to scope
      '='
        var(x) // search symbol table for x, starting with current, going up
        lit(10) // check (acceptable type?) ye
      '='
        var(x) //check ST, there is no x in current scope, so this is not a redec ~~> legal
        lit(A)
      print
        var(x) // we finish block, archive scope
```

SymbolTable
-----------
scope0
x val s1
----------  Block2, when we finish the block, we archive and delete this <<
scope1


Archive is used when converting Abstract Syntax Tree to intermediate code




  
